---
layout: base.njk
pageKey: about
title: About
permalink: about.html
description: Symbio AI is two builders turning plain-English ideas into websites, apps, and AI tools that help small businesses grow. If you can explain it, we can build it.
---

{# ===== Page head ====================================================== #}
<section class="section section--tight">
  <div class="container container--narrow center">
    <span class="eyebrow eyebrow--center">About Symbio AI</span>
    <h1 class="section__title">If you can explain it, we can build it.</h1>
    <p class="section__lead">
      Symbio AI is two builders. We turn plain-English ideas into websites, apps, and AI tools that
      help small businesses grow, without the agency runaround.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

{# ===== Vision ========================================================= #}
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid grid--2 grid--middle">
      <div data-reveal>
        <span class="eyebrow">Why we do this</span>
        <h2 class="section__title">Most small businesses are let down by their website.</h2>
        <p class="text-lead mt-6">
          It loads slowly, looks dated, or makes people work to get in touch, so visitors leave and
          you never hear from them. We fix the foundation first with a clean, fast site, then add
          booking, chat, and follow-up so the people who find you actually become customers. We keep
          it honest: a free scan before anyone talks money, real numbers, and software we’d happily
          use ourselves.
        </p>
      </div>

      <ul class="card__list" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1">
        <li>Plain English in, working software out.</li>
        <li>A free scan before anyone talks money.</li>
        <li>Honest pricing and realistic timelines.</li>
        <li>We build only what actually helps.</li>
        <li>You always have a direct line to the builders.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ===== Founders ====================================================== #}
<section class="section section--tint">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section__head" data-reveal>
      <span class="eyebrow">The team</span>
      <h2 class="section__title">Two people. Reachable directly.</h2>
      <p class="section__lead">No account managers, no hand-offs. You work with the people building it.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid--2">
      {% for person in site.founders %}
        <article class="founder" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="{{ loop.index0 }}">
          <span class="founder__avatar" aria-hidden="true">{{ person.name | first }}</span>
          <h3 class="founder__name">{{ person.name }}</h3>
          <p class="founder__role">{{ person.role }}</p>
          <div class="founder__contact">
            <a href="mailto:{{ person.email }}">✉ {{ person.email }}</a>
            {% if person.phone %}
              <a href="tel:{{ person.phone | replace(r/[^0-9+]/g, '') }}">☎ {{ person.phone }}</a>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ===== Process ======================================================= #}
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section__head section__head--center" data-reveal>
      <span class="eyebrow eyebrow--center">The process</span>
      <h2 class="section__title">Scan, plan, build, polish</h2>
      <p class="section__lead">A simple, honest path from “my site isn’t working” to “my site brings in work.”</p>
    </div>

    <ol class="grid grid--4">
      <li class="step" data-reveal>
        <span class="step__num">1</span>
        <h3 class="step__title">Scan</h3>
        <p class="step__text">
          We review your current site, for free, and tell you plainly what’s helping and what’s in
          the way.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="step" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1">
        <span class="step__num">2</span>
        <h3 class="step__title">Plan</h3>
        <p class="step__text">
          We agree on the smallest set of changes that will make the biggest difference, and price
          it honestly.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="step" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="2">
        <span class="step__num">3</span>
        <h3 class="step__title">Build</h3>
        <p class="step__text">
          We design and build it, with booking and chat wired in, and keep you posted as we go.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="step" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="3">
        <span class="step__num">4</span>
        <h3 class="step__title">Polish</h3>
        <p class="step__text">
          After launch we tune the copy, speed, and follow-ups until the site is pulling its weight.
        </p>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</section>

{# ===== Closing CTA =================================================== #}
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-band" data-reveal>
      <h2 class="cta-band__title">Tell us what you want to build</h2>
      <p class="cta-band__text">
        If you can explain it, we can build it. Start with a free scan, or email us directly.
      </p>
      <div class="btn-row btn-row--center">
        <a class="btn btn--light btn--lg" href="{{ site.cta.url }}">Get my free scan</a>
        <a class="btn btn--secondary btn--lg" href="mailto:{{ site.founders[0].email }}">Email the team</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
